data.description: Beautiful one story Ranch style home on .77 acres in Hueytown. Large fenced back yard with a 30x50 garage/ work shop and a covered 2 car carport / patio. Open floor plan with vaulted ceiling and cozy wood burning fireplace in kitchen and great room, allowing you to be in the kitchen and still enjoy your guests and family. Concrete counter top, stainless appliances, and more cabinet space than you could ever need. Large laundry room just off kitchen, separate formal dining room, and 5 bedrooms giving you all the room you need. Covered concrete area in back yard is great for entertaining, fire pits, or any other outdoor activity you have planned. Come visit your next home.
